            <caption>Figure 2. Front Bumper</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1>1. MOUNTING HOLES</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <para>The CE Series front bumper is a stylized wraparound steel bumper assembly. The wraparound design allows
            access for the tow hooks, and enhances the air flow to the radiator for better engine cooling.
        </para>
        <para>The front bumper is a one piece aerodynamically styled steel bumper. The bumper incorporates a swing out
            safety gate for passenger protection when entering or leaving the passenger compartment.
        </para>
